It would be good to add a defensive regression test for the hashCode,copyWith, == methods. Something like:
```
  test('AppBarTheme copyWith operator ==, hashCode basics()', () {
    expect(const AppBarTheme(), const AppBarTheme().copyWith()));
    expect(const TextTheme().hashCode, const AppBarTheme().copyWith().hashCode));
  });
```

